QuickFill - Your Ultimate Form Autofiller

Description:

QuickFill is a powerful Chrome extension designed to streamline the process of filling out online forms, saving you time and effort. Tired of repetitive typing? QuickFill is here to help! With just a few clicks, you can effortlessly complete forms with your saved information.

Features

1. Efficiency and Speed: QuickFill automates the form-filling process, significantly reducing the time you spend entering the same information over and over.

2. Free and Open Source: QuickFill is completely free to use and open source, allowing you to review and contribute to its development.

3. User-Friendly Interface: The extension features an intuitive interface that makes it easy to manage and use your saved information.


Say goodbye to tedious form filling and hello to QuickFill! Install QuickFill today and experience the convenience of effortless form completion. Visit our GitHub repository for more information and to contribute.
